			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,2,151</storyAction>
			<dialogue>151,徐庶:如今许都的上空妖气弥漫，就是因为在下假意祈祷之故。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>151,徐庶:孔明察觉这股妖气之后，自然会认定祈祷业已完成。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>151,徐庶:其实在下不过是让这股妖气，和魔王复活时的妖气一致罢了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,17</storyAction>
			<dialogue>17,貂蝉:您是说魔王复活的祈祷尚未进行吗？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,17</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,0,151</storyAction>
			<dialogue>151,徐庶:是的。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>187,黄巾兵:原来如此。也就是说孔明现在把注意力，完全放在北面的祭坛了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,151</storyAction>
			<dialogue>151,徐庶:北面的祭坛在五丈原。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,151</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,2,151</storyAction>
